sellerCard.description: HI, I'm Shah N., A Shopify expert designer and developer. I can help you to make professional, modern, fully functional Shopify website. I am passionate, experienced & problems solver web engineer. I will also assist you to provide best solution for your business or drop shipping store.

description.content:
Hey,

I'm Shah. A Shopify expert designer and developer. I can help you to make professional, modern, fully functional Shopify website. I will also assist you to provide best solutions for your business to be available online.


I've learned Shopify from a well reputed organization. and now I'm offering my expertise here.


What I am offering?

  • Shopify store creation
  • Niche and Product Research
  • Stunning logo/banner design
  • Product listing and categories creation
  • User-Friendly menus
  • Engageable, modern & nice store layout
  • Custom coded sections
  • PSD, FIGMA, XD to Shopify conversion
  • Conversion boost features such as Referral Rewards, Welcome discount, upsell options
  • SEO Friendly URLs/Titles
  • and much more to make your Shopify store to meet your business requirements.


4+ 1 reasons to choose me:

  1. On-Time Delivery
  2. Agile Updates
  3. Unlimited Revisions
  4. Premium Quality Guarantee
  5. 5+ Years Experience


If you have queries please feel free to reach out to me, I'll typically reply within one hour. Looking forward to work on your Shopify website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What Information do you need to get start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I need your Shopify store URL for accessing your store, the product information or niche, and some reference design. If you don't have anything I'll help you with all.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you use free or premium theme?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If you need to use some premium theme then you have to purchase that. Or I can utilized the free theme in a way So it will look premium quality.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you create a custom coded design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can create custom coded designs. you can send any design file like figma, PSD etc. I provide professional & optimal code solutions.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you make custom banners?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I'm doing ecommerce banner design in photoshop.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How about aftersale support?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes certainly, I'm offering VIP 15 days support. For example if you need to change any color, image, text, shipping settings on your Shopify etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I don't like your work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I always strive hard and smart to make your Shopify website like I'm doing work on my own website. But if we meet a situation where you don't like the work. I'll provide refund.
